## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="a1482-290"><xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataReader.GetOrdinal%2A> 第一次执行区分大小写查找。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a1482-290"><xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataReader.GetOrdinal%2A> performs a case-sensitive lookup first.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a1482-291">如果失败，进行第二个的不区分大小写搜索。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a1482-291">If it fails, a second case-insensitive search is made.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a1482-292">该方法将引发`IndexOutOfRange`异常，如果找不到从零开始的列序号。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a1482-292">The method throws an `IndexOutOfRange` exception if the zero-based column ordinal is not found.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="a1482-293"><xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataReader.GetOrdinal%2A> 不区分假名宽度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a1482-293"><xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataReader.GetOrdinal%2A> is kana-width insensitive.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="a1482-294">因为基于序号的查找比命名查找更有效，它是效率低下调用<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataReader.GetOrdinal%2A>在循环内。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a1482-294">Because ordinal-based lookups are more efficient than named lookups, it is inefficient to call <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataReader.GetOrdinal%2A> within a loop.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a1482-295">改为调用<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataReader.GetOrdinal%2A>一次，然后将分配给整数变量的结果，请使用在循环中。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a1482-295">Instead, call <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataReader.GetOrdinal%2A> once and then assign the results to an integer variable for use within the loop.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="a1482-296">下面的示例演示如何使用 <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataReader.GetOrdinal%2A> 方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a1482-296">The following example demonstrates how to use the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataReader.GetOrdinal%2A> method.</span></span>  
  
```vb  
Public Sub ReadOracleData(ByVal connectionString As String)  
  
    Dim queryString As String = "SELECT OrderID, CustomerID FROM Orders"  
    Dim connection As New OracleConnection(connectionString)  
    Dim command As New OracleCommand(queryString, connectionString)  
  
    connection.Open()  
  
    Dim reader As OracleDataReader = command.ExecuteReader()  
  
    Dim custIdCol As Integer = reader.GetOrdinal("CustomerID")  
  
    Do While reader.Read()  
        Console.WriteLine("CustomerID = {0}", reader.GetString(custIdCol))  
    Loop  
  
    reader.Close()  
    connection.Close()  
End Sub  
```  
  
```csharp  
public void ReadOracleData(string connectionString)  
{  
    string queryString = "SELECT OrderID, CustomerID FROM Orders";  
    OracleConnection connection = new OracleConnection(connectionString);  
    OracleCommand command = new OracleCommand(queryString,connection);  
  
    connection.Open();  
    OracleDataReader reader = command.ExecuteReader();  
  
    int custIdCol = reader.GetOrdinal("CustomerID");  
  
    while (reader.Read())  
        Console.WriteLine("CustomerID = {0}", reader.GetString(custIdCol));  
  
    reader.Close();  
    connection.Close();  
}  
```
